      <title>共和党获胜，最高法院保留共和党的裁决纽约地区</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/02/us/politics/supreme-court-malliotakis-new-york.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一项紧急裁决中，法官们保留了一名共和党女议员的选区，尽管下级法院裁定该选区非法削弱了少数族裔选民的权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/02/us/politics/supreme-court-malliotakis-new-york.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 01:45:25 GMT</pubDate>
